  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You manipulate the water and iron in the atmosphere to make two iron-rich aqua daggers that swirl around you in the air. As a bonus action, you can send out one dagger at a creature within 60 feet. Make a ranged ninjutsu attack, dealing 3d6 + your Ninjutsu ability modifier in piercing damage on hit. Once all daggers have been thrown, this jutsu ends</p><p>If your Ketsuryūgan is active while this jutsu is active, increase the damage die of each dagger by 1 step.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3, and the number of daggers created by +1.</p>",
